title: I can't get my pixel XL 4 to see my JBL Bluetooth headphones. Anyone else have this issue?
content: I have been through most all troubleshooting steps provided by Google help. I have no problem connecting to my phone to my vehicle. I have connected my head phone's to other phones in the house. With no luck of even seeing them on my new pixel XL 4. Any ideas would be great. I'm at my wit's end with this phone already...
